data.description: Here's a turn of the century home in the heart of Moline with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths.  You can be to shopping, restaurants and medical facilities within minutes.  In 2022 there was a new water line and sewer line installed from the street to the house.  Other updates include: roof 15 yr, HVAC 7 years, water heater 2 years, garden shed 2 years, electrical panel 5 years.  Backyard is fully fenced and there is both a front porch and a back deck for you to sit and enjoy the fresh air.  Appliances are negotiable with an acceptable offer.
